{"tid":1659364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[聲明] 請推到所有南亞朋友都睇到!!","createTime":"2019-10-17T02:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T13:29:49.000Z","uid":312164,"like":59,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"9a844d93a6f63c70f0241cc5461e06b181334993","tid":1659364,"uid":312164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:01:09.000Z","msg":"致所有南亞同路人：<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於港共政府對香港人的打壓無效，牠們極有可能再偽裝示威者以抹黑示威者之行為，因此作出以下聲明：<br />\n<br />\n示威者不會「裝修」:<br />\n1) 清真寺；<br />\n2) 重慶大廈；<br />\n3) 南亞人店鋪；及<br />\n不會無差別攻擊無辜南亞市民。<br />\n<br />\n----------<br />\n<br />\nTo all South Asian friends,<br />\n<br />\nDue to plans to suppress protesters by the so-called government, it&rsquo;s highly possible that undercover cops will try to frame protesters with violent behaviors. Protesters hereby declare that:<br />\n<br />\nProtesters will NOT damage:<br />\n1) the Kowloon Masjid and Islamic Centre;<br />\n2) the Chungking Mansions;<br />\n3) shops owned by South Asians civilians; and<br />\nWILL NOT indiscriminately assault South Asians.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmkKtdE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmkKtdE.jpg&h=6d5e00cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FyqKteL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFyqKteL.jpg&h=0c461b68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QFWmvs6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQFWmvs6.jpg&h=50aae8cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uxOoJN7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuxOoJN7.jpg&h=4a9e99fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">10.20 尖沙咀見!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"ba3858ff8470570326c79ffa59f70c14ae2301d4","tid":1659364,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:01:35.000Z","msg":"【再次有圖有真相】令街坊知道1020遊行嘅最佳方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657842</a>"},{"pid":"62fd07bbb9d679ae1b3c90e791a40a3864fc17c0","tid":1659364,"uid":165515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:01:51.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"fc3301db79ebe06e9b095447d088e8ecc9b8d178","tid":1659364,"uid":312164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:02:40.000Z","msg":"10.20 尖沙咀見"},{"pid":"fdc03b785d9b4a42a4e3f1131e7948f87d5193c2","tid":1659364,"uid":312164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:04:13.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔郁 請幫推!"},{"pid":"e2f9adef0bb5109e4546442206c652f240a03333","tid":1659364,"uid":312164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:06:02.000Z","msg":"唔該幫推!"},{"pid":"234de95757381178dc569298fa29b624104914ae","tid":1659364,"uid":312164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:07:27.000Z","msg":"幫推呀呀呀呀"},{"pid":"7851378a671cbb5095f4086a5bd32cb048563203","tid":1659364,"uid":312164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:09:52.000Z","msg":"推我上去"},{"pid":"8bccff360554ce2b0a775116292903cc3ac2518c","tid":1659364,"uid":312164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62fd07bbb9d679ae1b3c90e791a40a3864fc17c0","tid":1659364,"uid":165515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:01:51.000Z","msg":"1"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:10:49.000Z","msg":"唔該幫手推"},{"pid":"92b31178249ad2beb830589d93fd18acd59eeb77","tid":1659364,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/